overview:
TwitFile.com lets easily you share files on Twitter, and these can amount to as much as 200 MB per file for completely free. This means that you will be capable of putting any file you might want to share with others across in real time, and letting others procure them no matter where they are located, and without having to rely on any e-mail client.
